Excellent Vince performance A beautiful show all around.  Definitely not rushed with a pace that allows everybody to stand out.  Excellent audio quality that reveals a lot of Vince in the vocals and instrumental mix.  Jerry's playing is quite adept for later years, beautiful phrasing and clarity.  Bob and Phil are not overwhelmingly up front, but it's nice to hear Jerry carrying the heaviest laod with Vince right with him.  Sweet performance.
- Average good show, with Hornsby showcased.
